  <name>MfaText</name>
  <summary>A feature-rich text editor for GNOME</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      MfaText is a feature-rich text editor for GNOME that can be used
      both as a standalone application and as a library module for integration
      into PyGObject applications.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Syntax highlighting for many programming languages</li>
      <li>Search and replace functionality</li>
      <li>Undo/redo support</li>
      <li>Line numbers</li>
      <li>Word wrap</li>
      <li>Auto-indentation</li>
      <li>File monitoring for external changes</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
